Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Camel Rock
Description: A large rock that looks like the humps on a camel that has a surf spot right next to it.

Name: Tomo Japanese Restaurant
Description: A delicious sushi restaurant that serves an excellent spicy salmon skin roll.

Name: Kimtu Swimming Hole
Description: One of many locations where people can access the Trinity River and go swimming during the summertime.

Name: Doheney State Beach
Description: A family-friendly beach with a picnic area, volleyball courts, and fun waves to surf.

Name: Santa Barbara's Surf  N' Wear Beach House
Description: One of Santa Barbara's best surf shops that sells surfboards, wetsuits, clothing, and more!
